show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/EzuXrv
show.description: Meera, a resilient woman with a mysterious past, and Kunal, a powerful businessman torn between logic and destiny. When twin children appear with an uncanny connection to Meera, a chain of emotional upheavals, hidden truths, and shifting loyalties unfolds. As family secrets unravel and trust is tested, Meera and Kunal must confront their pasts to protect their future.
